Generative Art Tool

A tool to facilitate procedural drawing to procedurally laid out nodes

number data:
single number
array of numbers
a function returning a single number or array of numbers

matrix data:
same as number data but replace number with matrix

node : {
  x: number,
  y: number,
  rotation: number,
  regX: number,
  regY: number,
  width: number,
  height: number,
  transform: matrix,
  drawCommands: commands,
  childData: {
    x: number data,
    y: number data,
    rotation: number data,
    regX: number data,
    regY: number data,
    width: number data,
    height: number data,
    transform: matrix data,
    drawCommands: draw command data,
    layoutCommands: layout command data
  }
  childNodes: array of nodes populated with childData
}
